entries.content: AIntivirus is a cryptocurrency project founded by Janice McAfee and a team closely connected to the legendary tech pioneer, John McAfee. AIntivirus provides several services designed for privacy and cross-chain utility: Cross-Chain Mixer for anonymous transfers across SOL–SOL, ETH–ETH, SOL–ETH, and AINTI variants. Bridge to swap tokens between Solana and Ethereum. Gift Cards & e-SIMs purchasable with AINTI with no KYC. And much more! In addition to all the products and services you can buy with the AINTI token, holders of AINTI enjoy multiple other benefits: Burn Mechanism: A portion of fees from all products is burned, reducing circulating supply and potentially increasing scarcity.DAO Voting Rights: Influence future project decisions and features.Eligibility for Airdrops: Participate in NFT and other community airdrops. A portion of every fee derived from AIntivirus’s products and services—notably mixers, bridges, e-SIMs, and merch—is used to burn AINTI tokens. This mechanism is designed to steadily reduce supply as usage grows. Solana: BAezfVmia8UYLt4rst6PCU4dvL2i2qHzqn4wGhytpNJWEthereum: 0x686c5961370Db7F14F57f5a430e05DeaE64df504DO NOT FALL FOR SCAMS. Official Contract Address Verify and interact securely with the authentic Aintivirus token — honoring John McAfee's legacy of freedom, privacy, decentralized power, resilience, rebellion, and innovation. The John McAfee archive is a curated vault of his works — from books that capture his radical ideas, to archived videos, including the infamous Mixology series.

Bold, unfiltered, and unforgettable, this collection preserves John’s legacy in its rawest form. Ainti Surveillance Merch Drop Ainti will release its first line of physical merchandise designed to highlight anti-surveillance culture. A free airdrop of a digital NFT 'receipt book and video series' tied to the legend John McAfee Mixology videos. The Adventures Of John McAfee Animated Series (Season 1) A highly stylized and satirical animated series chronicling the wild and infamous life of John McAfee. Season 1 explores his time creating McAfee Antivirus, his later controversial antics, evasion from authorities, and cryptic public statements. Ainti EXIF Data Removal Tool A tool that removes metadata from images, videos, and files — preventing users from unintentionally revealing GPS location, timestamps, camera models, and other identifying data. Ainti True Crime Mini-Series Narrated By John McAfee (Season 1) A documentary-style animated series exploring true crime stories from the digital underworld, narrated using archival audio and AI-generated voiceovers of John McAfee. Season 1 explores hacks, whistleblowing, darknet markets, and state surveillance scandals. The Adventures Of John McAfee Animated Series (Season 2) Continuation of the animated series.

Season 2 dives deeper into McAfee’s time on the run, his presidential campaign, his crypto evangelism, and his messages in his final days. Mixer Version 2 With Staking An upgrade to Ainti’s mixer platform, improving transaction anonymization, speed, and usability. The new version introduces staking — allowing users to lock up tokens in return for rewards. Running With Scissors – Season 3 The third installment of AINTIVIRUS chaotic, underground docuseries exploring the wild life of John McAfee. Ainti True Crime Mini-Series Narrated By John McAfee (Season 2) Season 2 of the narrated true crime series expands the scope of digital and political crimes, focusing on international cryptocurrency cases, drugs, and cyber warfare. Surveillance Poster Campaign A physical street campaign that blends surveillance awareness with real world interactions. Each poster will have a QR code. When scanned, it will display a video, and burn AINTI. The First Major AINTI DAO Proposal Launch of the first governance votes for the AINTI decentralized autonomous organization. Public Dashboards for All Products A new suite of public analytics dashboards visualizing ecosystem usage across mixers, swaps, and bridges, and more!

A live portal showing global data collection patterns. Interactive map of trackers, cameras, and more! John McAfee Memorabilia Auction An on chain auction of personal items of John McAfee that he had both while on the run and in prison. 25% of the proceeds will be used to buy AINTI. Announce New Partnerships Reveal of strategic alliances with privacy aligned projects and companies. VPN, Email, Data deletion services and more. Stablecoin/Privacy Coin On-Chain Exchange Launch of a privacy native DEX connecting stable coins and Monero, ZCash and more. Will support Matrix blockchain. AINTIVIRUS Privacy Wallet featuring the Aintivirus bridge, exchange, built in mixer, eSIM, and gift systems all in one encrypted interface. An emergency response privacy app. One tap kill switch for wiping devices and all back ups. Local Privacy-Focused LLM Offline AI engine for text, voice, and image processing. AINTIVIRUS Browser Extension A privacy layer for all browsers. Blocks trackers, metadata, fingerprinting scripts, and more! Anonymous Signal Signup We provide an eSIM number so users can receive the one time verification code for signing up to Signal without exposing their real phone number.
